# Jirani OS website — environment variables
#
# The site is currently a static marketing site with no backend
# integrations, so nothing here is required to run or build it. This file
# establishes the pattern for when real integrations are added (contact
# form submission, pricing waitlist capture, analytics).

# Example: a real endpoint for the Contact page and Pricing waitlist form
# to POST to, once one exists (currently both forms are client-side only).
# VITE_CONTACT_FORM_ENDPOINT=

# Example: an analytics/telemetry write key, if one is added later.
# VITE_ANALYTICS_KEY=

# Example: the canonical site URL, used by lib/seo.ts for absolute OG URLs.
VITE_SITE_URL=https://jiranios.com
